      • getComponent

        <T> T getComponent(UniProtData.ComponentType type)
        The return type depends on UniProtData.ComponentType
        type: COMMENTS: return: list of UniProt Comment
        type: FEATURES: return: list of UniProt Feature
        type: GENES: return: list of UniProt Gene
        type: XREFS: return: list of UniProt DatabaseCrossReference
        type: ECNUMBER: return: list of UniProt ec number String
        type: PROTEIN_NAMES: return: list of UniProt protein name String
        type: KEYWORDS: return: list of UniProt Keyword
        type: TAXONOMY: return: list of UniProt NcbiTaxon
        Parameters:
        type - UniProtData.ComponentType to return
        Returns:
        T the generic component corresponding to the type, or null otherwise
